properties.Name: RatePlan
properties.Description:
A contract that describes the conditions of wireless service including all fees and usage allowances.

A predefined tariff or billing structure for the billing of Special Services, Air Time and related Carrier services and products to Customers.

Columns.Name: RatePlanId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a product.

Columns.Name: RatePlanName
Columns.Description: The common name or business name by which a Rate Plan is known.

Columns.Name: RatePlanDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Rate Plan.

Columns.Name: RatePlanEffectiveDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Rate Plan is in effect.

Columns.Name: RatePlanStrategyStatement
Columns.Description:
The strategy statement describing why the Rate Plan was created or conceived.

- Who is it meant to cater to or attract?

- What market or market segment is it intended to address?

- What revenues are meant to be enhanced and by how much?

- How does the Rate Plan increase competitiveness?

Columns.Name: RatePlanEligibilityStatement
Columns.Description: A description of the eligibility requirements and restrictions that apply for the Rate Plan.

Columns.Name: BasicMonthlyCostAmount
Columns.Description: The basic monthly charge for the Rate Plan before additional charges are applied.

Columns.Name: RatePlanCategoryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Rate Plan Category.

Columns.Name: StandardContractPeriod
Columns.Description: The standard contract period expressed in days for which the Rate Plan is normally issued or sold.

Columns.Name: MinimumContractPeriod
Columns.Description: The least amount of time for which a Rate Plan agreement is valid.

Columns.Name: RatePlanStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Rate Plan Status.

Columns.Name: RatePlanTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Rate Plan Type.
